TEXT 
ctrl + arrows                    ---> jump
shift + arrows                   ---> select 
ctrl + backspace                 ---> delete a word

CHROME
alt + arrows                      ---> back n forth
ctrl + t                          ---> new tab
ctrl + shift + t                  ---> open deleted tabs
ctrl + tab || ctrl + shift + tab  ---> jump tabs
ctrl + r                          ---> refresh 

WINDOWS
alt + tab                         ---> jumps
win + arrows                      ---> layout
win + d                           ---> minimise and vice-versa
alt + f4                          ---> delete 
win + n                           ---> open taskbar app

FILES
f2                                ---> rename
ctrl + shift + n                  ---> new folder

OTHERS
win + l                           ---> lock 
win + i                           ---> settings
win + a                           ---> action center

VIRTUAL DESKTOP
win + ctrl + d                    ---> create 
win + ctrl + right/left arrows    ---> switch 
win + ctrl + f4                   ---> delete 
